                "# Sequence Modify Maths Operators",
                "",
                "In this notebook you will edit working programs so they use maths operators correctly.",
                "",
                "## What you will practise",
                "- Floor division `//` to get whole groups only.",
                "- Modulus `%` to find what is left over.",
                "- `round(value, places)` to control decimal places.",
                "",
                "## How to work",
                "1. Read the task and expected output carefully.",
                "2. Change the starter code so the output matches exactly.",
                "3. Focus on the operator named in each task.",
                "4. Keep your code in sequence only: no `if`, loops, or functions.",
                ""
            ]
        },
