                "## Exercise 7 \u2014 Split minutes into hours and minutes",
                "",
                "**Working code:**",
                "```python",
                "minutes = 125",
                "hours = minutes / 60",
                "minutes_left = minutes - 60",
                "print(str(minutes) + \" minutes is \" + str(hours) + \" hours and \" + str(minutes_left) + \" minutes\")",
                "```",
                "",
                "**Task:** Change `hours` to use floor division `//` for full hours. Then use modulus `%` for `minutes_left` so it shows only the leftover minutes.",
                "",
                "**Expected output:**",
                "```",
                "125 minutes is 2 hours and 5 minutes",
                "```",
                ""
